cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Reflexive Coherence Agentic Ecology"
message: "If you use this repository, please cite it as below and cite the specific paper, specification section, or related RC repository that your work depends on."
abstract: "Mixed-license conceptual paper/specification repository: papers/ documents declare CC BY-SA 4.0 in their headers; non-paper support files are GPL-2.0-only unless a file states otherwise. The repository translates classical state-rule agent systems into Reflexive Coherence agentic ecologies and translates message-first coordination into shared-medium participation. It includes RC-Ant Colony as the first worked example, with explicit producer-residue, naturalization-debt, message-scaffold, and medium-debt claim boundaries."
authors:
